- install express-validator for validation: npm install --save express-validator
- install mongoose for database: npm install --save mongoose
- install multer for parsing image : npm install --save multer
- install uuid to generate a unique id for date fix with images: npm install --save uuid
- install bcryptjs which allows us to hash a password in a secure way : npm install --save bcryptjs
- install jsonwebtoken for creating json web tokens used for authentication: npm install --save jsonwebtoken   


